title: Grateful Dead Live at Greek Theatre, U. Of California on 1982-05-22
description:
Set 1

Jack Straw-> Sugaree, Cassidy, Tennessee Jed-> Minglewood Blues, Cumberland Blues, Lazy Lightning-> Supplication-> Deal

Set 2

China Cat Sunflower-> I Know You Rider-> Women Are Smarter, Good Time Blues, Lost Sailor-> Saint Of Circumstance-> He's Gone-> Drums-> Not Fade Away-> Wharf Rat-> Around & Around-> Good Lovin', E: U.S. Blues

reviews.review_text: WOW Phenomenal recording/matrix! Sounds like you're actually in the building with the band. Thanks!!!
ANOTHER MILLER/SEAMONS GEM! This is one of the best matrix recordings I have ever heard! Another Grateful Greek show!
Deal For some reason Deal won't play. :(
